local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local MessageBox = require "actions/MessageBox" local Animate = require "actions/Animate" local Do = require "actions/Do" local PlayAudio = require "actions/PlayAudio"
return function(self) if not GameState:isFlagSet("b_speech") then return MessageBox {message = "Locked.", blocking = true} else return Serial { PlayAudio("sfx", "openchasm", 1.0, true), Animate(self.sprite, "opening"), Animate(self.sprite, "open"), Do(function() self:removeCollision() end) } end end

local Action = require "actions/Action"
return function(self) if GameState:isFlagSet(self) then self.sprite:setAnimation("open") self:removeCollision() end return Action() end

local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local MessageBox = require "actions/MessageBox" local Animate = require "actions/Animate" local Do = require "actions/Do" local PlayAudio = require "actions/PlayAudio"
return function(self) self.scene.player:removeKeyHint() return MessageBox {message = "Locked.", blocking = true} end

local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local Animate = require "actions/Animate" local PlayAudio = require "actions/PlayAudio" local Do = require "actions/Do"
return function(self) return Serial { PlayAudio("sfx", "openchasm", 1.0, true), Animate(self.sprite, "opening"), Animate(self.sprite, "open"), Do(function() GameState:setFlag(self) self:removeCollision() end) } end

local Serial = require "actions/Serial" local MessageBox = require "actions/MessageBox" local Animate = require "actions/Animate" local Do = require "actions/Do"
return function(self) local walkout, walkin, sprites = self.scene.player:split() self.scene.player:removeKeyHint() self.scene.player.cinematicStack = self.scene.player.cinematicStack + 1 return Serial { walkout, Animate(sprites.sonic.sprite, "idleup"), Animate(sprites.sally.sprite, "idleup"), MessageBox {message = "Sally: Definitely not under Robotnik's control...", blocking = true}, Animate(sprites.sonic.sprite, "pose"), MessageBox {message = "Sonic: These are my kinda people!", blocking = true}, walkin, Do(function() self.scene.player.x = self.scene.player.x + 60 self.scene.player.y = self.scene.player.y + 60 self.scene.player.cinematicStack = self.scene.player.cinematicStack - 1 end) } end
